    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, offering exceptional linear power delivery. Power is managed via a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system overhaul, ensuring long-term chassis rigidity and precise valve timing. The suspension kinematics remain sharp, providing the communicative steering and lateral composure expected of the M-chassis. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain and throttle response are perfectly synchronized for the purist seeking an analog experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
