    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly dependable vehicle that has been treated with care and consistency. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, maintaining a high-gloss luster; while there are minor cosmetic imperfections such as small stone chips on the front fascia and a few light car-wash swirls, the body remains straight and free of any significant dents. Step inside to a cabin that feels fresh and inviting. The upholstery is in excellent shape with only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control, infotainment system, and heated seats\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the vehicle is mechanically robust. It has followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule, with the most recent service including a synthetic oil change, new air filters, and a cooling system flush. The transmission delivers crisp, smooth shifts, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. The sale includes a complete set of service records, the original window sticker, and two remote key fobs. This is an honest, well-sorted car that offers a premium driving experience without the premium price tag.",
